{"tha-ap488:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap488:0.2":"Pamsukulavagga ","tha-ap488:0.3":"Dhatupujakattheraapadana ","tha-ap488:1.1":"“Nibbute lokanathamhi, ","tha-ap488:1.2":"siddhatthe lokanayake; ","tha-ap488:1.3":"Mama nati samanetva, ","tha-ap488:1.4":"dhatupujam akasaham. ","tha-ap488:2.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap488:2.2":"yam dhatumabhipujayim; ","tha-ap488:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap488:2.4":"dhatupujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap488:3.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap488:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap488:3.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap488:4.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap488:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap488:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap488:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap488:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap488:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap488:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma dhatupujako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap488:7.1":"Dhatupujakattherassapadanam chattham. "}